🎱 The Eight by 8 Build Challenge 🎱

We’ve had many chances to build upon the glorious expanse that build plates present, but what happens when the walls close in?

An 8 by Eight challenge.

All Challengers must create their ideal 8x8 build. Bring your A-game, Compact your builds. Let’s see what wonderful creativity can be had in the Eight!

:timer: Challenge dates: September 22, 2020 – October 6th, 2020 at 6 PM PT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! Challenge theme is open to interpretation.
:sign: Post your images or video submission and buildplate share link in #custom-adventure-challenge by the end date. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges_og: Submissions may be used in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!

messages.content:
8️⃣ The walls closed in! You were challenged to build on an 8x8 buildplate. Did you panic? My sources say no! You reached into your inventory and crafted some marvelous creations utilizing every block of your plates. From a magnificent tower to Creeper statues to eerie graves and more… you definitely showed us your imagination knows no bounds! 🤯 

:challenges: Is it time to found out which #the-8x8-challenge builds you voted as your favorite? Signs point to yes.
:diamond: @Dreoxur - Zen Islands
:gold: @Frahst - Nature's Secrets  (*Tie!*)
:gold: @Gurgensson - Jump Jump Mobs!  (*Tie!*)
:iron: @bigboypants321 - Pig Jungle Habitat

**Congratulations to the winners! And thank you to everyone who participated!** Submissions may be featured in social media posts. Checkout all the compact builds in the 📌 pinned messages. :dancing_parrot:

Blog post for this challenge is up! Quick, tell your friends!
https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/minecraft-earth-challenge--8x8
